id=moon-ssh
name=Moon SSH Autostart
version=v0.4.0
versionCode=5
author=jay
description=Enters the Ubuntu 26.04 chroot at /data/data/com.termux/files/home/ubuntu once at boot and runs the hooks in /etc/host-hooks/*.hook (lexical order, as root). Ships 10-sshd + 20-tailscale enabled, 50-agents disabled. Disable a hook by renaming it to *.hook.disabled. Log at /var/log/moon-ssh-boot.log (in-chroot path; preamble at /data/local/tmp/moon-ssh-boot.log until the chroot path is reachable).
